window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Kristjan's home was attacked. He was supposed to be sent through a portal with his guard to keep him safe until everything settled down, but things didn't go as planned. </b></p> <p>He woke up without his memory in a world that is filled with Demons, Djinns, Phoenix, Fire Giants, and many others.</p> <p>During his time on Exhulm, he's bullied for being a non-magical being, making his life difficult. Around his 18th birthday, things begin to change, though. His magic presents itself, making his life even<i> more</i> problematic. Kristjan realizes that maybe not having magic wasn't so bad after all.</p>"; 
